  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 5ad1d7fb7f6172a45b05986fb296a635, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: '::'
  dialogueText: {fileID: 1461506044}
  dialogueLines:
  - Welcome to the login page!
  - First, try any value you think is correct
  - 'Now try <color=red>admin''--</color>  '
  - See how the rest of the query becomes a comment
  - 'Now click the login button to enter '
  - Good job
  - but what if you dont have any username?
  - Easy!
  - ' try <color=red>'' OR 1=1 --</color>'
  - Because 1=1 is always true
  - Good job soldier!
  - You can also <color=#B83D00>Inject Malicious SQL</color>!
  - use <color=#B83D00>name'); DELETE FROM users;</color>
  - Even if the username is wrong, the DELETE query will still run
  - Nice work
  - Now complete all your missions!
  typingSpeed: 0.05
  waitNextLine: 1.5
